To build a deployable version of this service, use the command:

$ sbt assembly

This will build a single jar file that can be run.

To run the service, you need to provide it with configuration, typically as a properties file.
An example file is in src/main/resources/data-exporting-service.properties.example.
Edit this as necessary, then leave it on the classpath when you run the service.

To run the service, use a command like this:

$ java -cp .:data-exporter-service-assembly-1.0.jar com.blinkboxbooks.mimir.export.DataExporterService
